==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Oppositely
<hw>Op"po*site*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a situation to face each
other; in an opposite manner or direction; adversely.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Winds from all quarters <qex>oppositely</qex> blow.</q>
<rj><qau>May.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Oppositeness</ent>⟦br⟧
